Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.27,0:23:19.77,ED,,0,0,0,,NA NA NA~
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.77,0:23:23.73,ED,,0,0,0,,你是不是发胖了?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.73,0:23:29.82,ED,,0,0,0,,吵死了 这是进化啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.32,0:23:33.24,ED,,0,0,0,,来吧 大闹一场咯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.24,0:23:34.99,ED,,0,0,0,,可别怪我不客气
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.99,0:23:36.95,ED,,0,0,0,,瞄准未来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.95,0:23:38.41,ED,,0,0,0,,锁定目标Kiss and GO
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.41,0:23:40.46,ED,,0,0,0,,Life is wonderful
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.46,0:23:42.50,ED,,0,0,0,,更有欲望一点
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.50,0:23:44.29,ED,,0,0,0,,如果没有悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.29,0:23:46.25,ED,,0,0,0,,那也就没有乐趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.25,0:23:48.01,ED,,0,0,0,,没有人能夺走
